Author: polycryptoblog#1173
Content: Rewards decentralize coin generation to the hold in a much more equitable way than mining or staking ,  the purpose is to be active user rewards , else a global demurrage effect will occur,  which effectively lowers the bounds of coin supply per given year

Author: polycryptoblog#1173
Content: TLDR: users have to be active in their coin holdings to take advantage of coin generation profitability

Content: Yes

Content: Exactly

Content: There is a compound effect in reduced emissions
